The paper also mentions comparisons of ACL2 with other systems, which could place it in the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category. Furthermore, the paper discusses the improvements and extensions to the theorem prover, which could make it relevant to the Emerging Technologies (cs.ET) sub-category. Finally, the paper includes peer-reviewed technical papers, which could make it relevant to the Measurement and Analysis (cs.MS) sub-category.
